{"tid":2014782,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"標普：香港評級被下調風險急劇上升","createTime":"2020-05-13T08:43:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T04:45:30.000Z","uid":240362,"like":654,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":124,"replies":[{"pid":"31d8565e82f3d787a804a3d742387b810c03255c","tid":2014782,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T08:43:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1525924-20200513.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1525924-20200513.htm&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9NQ9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=a5804af2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1525924-20200513.htm&h=04c17ea6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1525924-20200513.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n評級機構標準普爾主權與國際公共產業融資部副董事尹睿指，目前維持香港信用評級「AA+」，但內地經濟下行以及最近重燃的社會事件，將繼續衝擊零售行業，近日香港被下調評級的風險急劇上升，與區內其他地方一致。她又指，政府動用財政儲備推出抗疫措施，或會進一步削弱未來信貸實力。<br />\n<br />\n另外，標普指，疫情大流行打擊香港經濟，預期今年本港經濟將收縮3.9%，明年回升至增長4.8%。<br />\n<br />\n標普全球評級亞太區經濟學家Vishrut Rana認為，隨著疫情緩和，政府逐步解除限制，加上內地經濟正常化，或會重新刺激本地消費，但歐美經濟深度收縮將會波及香港，加上香港經濟依賴旅遊業，相信復元時間較長，最少需要1年。"},{"pid":"3770934645494e8ce952390edea0b6cf818b252a","tid":2014782,"uid":2054,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T08:44:09.000Z","msg":"快啦"},{"pid":"2c225bca71dd7c942e7a71d1646ff72c2c196326","tid":2014782,"uid":21661,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T08:44:50.000Z","msg":"等咩喎"},{"pid":"84f89c50e07e60e8e7718a5790b3df3dc31f7082","tid":2014782,"uid":89641,"like":142,"dislike":5,"score":137,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T08:45:29.000Z","msg":"睇錯成評級急劇上升，心諗啲鬼佬中左邪？<br />\n<br />\n好彩係我自己眼殘（老啦老啦）"},{"pid":"008646990b5ef60f5140d9213d3b99be6d05c70c","tid":2014782,"uid":107577,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T08:45:30.000Z","msg":"我最期待嘅畫面出現了.gif"},{"pid":"900d950f4da268ee61dca48d2d517d4df2a11c